<h2> Welcome <%=current_user.username %>! </h2>
<h4> Use the Nav Bar on top to go to your desired page! Here are somethings you can do...</h4>
<ul>
    <li>View Your Routines</li>
    <li>Create a New Routine</li>
    <li>Look at Comments on Routines</li>
    <li>Comment on Other Routines</li>
    <li>And much more! Take a look around!</li>
</ul>

<h1>  Here are all Routines! </h1>

<% if @routines.empty? %>
    <h2> No Routines yet! </h2>
<% else %>
<ul>
    <% @routines.each do |i| %>
        <li> <%= link_to i.day, "/routines/#{i.id}" %> day - has <%= i.comments.size%> comments </li>
    <% end %>
</ul>
<% end %>
